_sText:
These maps are my first maps ever publicated so don't be to demanding please. The most elaborated map is Achievements_nade_t. I think it's a good idea but it isn't perfect. This is de version 1 of the maps. I will update them later!

The folder that you will download is compound by four maps (plus two texts and one picture):

	- Achievements_t_weapons;
	- Achievements_ct_weapons;
	- Achievements_nade_t;
	- Achievements_bomb;

This four maps can be used for almost all achievements you can do, but NOT ALL!

The name indication [_t_weapons or nade_t or _ct_weapons] is the name team that you need to go if you wont to complete it faster.

Recomendations:

	- Start the game and run a private server without bots;
	- Write in console: bot_add_ct (if you are in terrorist team), bot_add_t (if you are in ct team);
	- If the private server goes down, don't worry, is just an update;
	- Now type in console again this three commands (be sure that is one bot in the other team): mp_autoteambalance 0, mp_limitteams 20, bot_knives_only;
	- Then type bot_add_(other team name t or ct) until the team gets full.

NOW YOU ARE READY TO GET 90% OF THE ACHIEVEMENTS!!!

	- If you wont, you can put teammates but it will be harder to get the achievements.

I think that is all, tank you for reading this and any questions you might have, just ask me. Have fun!

